Package: banqueHydro
Type: Package
Title: Collection of data data from the banque hydro website
Version: 0.1.0
Author: lise.vaudor@ens-lyon.fr, david.dorchies@irstea.fr, maxime.jay-allemand@irstea.fr
Maintainer: Lise Vaudor <lise.vaudor@ens-lyon.fr>
Description: This package uses the banque hydro website to collect discharge data from gauging stations throughout France.
    It uses scraping techniques to collect QJM and QTVAR data.
